what is a design system
-a design system is a comprehensive set of guidelines, principles, and resusable components that are made to facilitate the creation, of digital products
>assets library like icons font etc
>components/patterns libraries
>storybook docs?


why building unique design system for sqli
>fast delivery: speed up design and development cycles and save time by having resulable components
>reduce redundancy: build it one time and reusite thousands of time and changing the source (DS) will affect all users.
>foster quality: better UX/UI, accessibility, performance and responsiveness

design system challenges
>maintaining consistency across members and projects
>balancing dlexibility and standardization
>Managing updates and version control


